     H            Y.
     F** UEXR29B ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: CHECK ORDER EXISTS (BY PP10)              *
     F*
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2024.01.24                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR29B'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $NKOJ   1
     F*                    PARM           $NUKE   4
     F*                    PARM           $NOHZ   8
     F*                    PARM           $NOBN   2
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN  20
     F*                    PARM           $ODRN  10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*      $NKOJ :  1A FACTORY
     F*      $NUKE :  4A DOCK
     F*      $NOHZ :  8A SHIP DATE
     F*      $NOBN :  2A BIN#
     F*      $MHIN : 20A USER PART#
     F*      $ODRN : 10A ORDER#
     F*  OUT $RTN  :  1A RETURN CODE (Y:EXIST, N:NOT)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PL10DIF  E           K        DISK
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 KMHIN
     I                                        1   5 KMHN1
     I                                        6  10 KMHN2
     I                                       11  15 KMHN3
     I                                       16  20 KMHN4
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80KNOHZ
     I                                        1   40KNOYY
     I                                        5   60KNOMM
     I                                        7   80KNODD
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * CHECK PP100
     C           K#PP10    CHAINAB#PL10D             98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL'Y'       $RTN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL'N'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $NKOJ   1
     C                     PARM           $NUKE   4
     C                     PARM           $NOHZ   8
     C                     PARM           $NOBN   2
     C                     PARM           $MHIN  20
     C                     PARM           $ODRN  10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           K#PP10    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KNONY   40
     C                     KFLD           KNOYY   40
     C                     KFLD           KNOMM   20
     C                     KFLD           KNODD   20
     C                     KFLD           KNOBN   20
     C                     KFLD           KMHN1   5
     C                     KFLD           KMHN2   5
     C                     KFLD           KMHN3   5
     C                     KFLD           KMHN4   5
     C                     KFLD           KODRN  10
     C                     KFLD           KNKOJ   1
     C                     KFLD           KNUKE   4
      * SET KEYS
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     KNONY
     C                     MOVEL$NKOJ     KNKOJ
     C                     MOVEL$NUKE     KNUKE
     C                     MOVEL$NOHZ     KNOHZ
     C                     MOVEL$NOBN     KNOBN
     C                     MOVEL$MHIN     KMHIN
     C                     MOVEL$ODRN     KODRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
